---
// TrustSection.astro
// Redesigned "Approved By" section for construction company
// Registered by FBR and PRA
---

<section class="relative bg-bgDark1 w-full py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">

  <!-- Subtle background grid texture -->
  

  <!-- Top border accent -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[3px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="content-container relative z-10 fade-in">

    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block text-blue-400 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">
        ✦ Verified & Trusted ✦
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-primaryText text-4xl sm:text-5xl 2xl:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Officially
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-200 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent"> Recognized</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Our company stands on a foundation of legal compliance, financial integrity, and government-verified credentials.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards Row -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">

      <!-- FBR Card -->
      <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 hover:border-orange-500/40 hover:bg-white/8 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 right-8 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400/60 to-transparent"></div>
        
        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20 rounded-full px-3 py-1 mb-6">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-400 animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="text-orange-400 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Federal</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Logo / Acronym -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/20 to-orange-600/20 border border-orange-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-orange-400 text-xl font-black tracking-tight">FBR</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Federal Board<br/>of Revenue</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Registered and compliant with the Federal Board of Revenue. All tax records are verified and up-to-date under FBR regulations, ensuring full federal tax compliance.
        </p>

        <!-- Verified tick -->
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="text-green-400 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">Taxpayer Record Satisfied</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PRA Card -->
      <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 hover:border-orange-500/40 hover:bg-white/8 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 right-8 h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400/60 to-transparent"></div>

        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20 rounded-full px-3 py-1 mb-6">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-400 animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="text-orange-400 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Provincial</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Logo / Acronym -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/20 to-orange-600/20 border border-orange-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-orange-400 text-xl font-black tracking-tight">PRA</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Punjab Revenue<br/>Authority</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Fully registered with the Punjab Revenue Authority. Our provincial tax obligations are satisfied and actively maintained in compliance with PRA standards.
        </p>

        <!-- Verified tick -->
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="text-green-400 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">Taxpayer Record Satisfied</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom trust bar -->
    <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 sm:gap-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500 text-sm">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500/70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
        </svg>
        Government Registered Since 1990
      </div>
      <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-5 bg-white/10"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500 text-sm">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500/70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"/>
        </svg>
        All Tax Records Up-to-Date
      </div>
      <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-5 bg-white/10"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-500 text-sm">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500/70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3"/>
        </svg>
        Fully Compliant Operations
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Bottom border accent -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-[3px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-orange-500 to-transparent"></div>
</section>